---
Slots:
 service: alignment, oil change, routine, tires, brakes, repair, other
  restrictions: only output the one-word categories listed under "service". the only exception to this is "other". For "other", include a brief description of the service requested
 model: SUV, sedan, compact, electric
  restrictions: only output from the list in "model". If not specified, do not output this slot at all. 
 year: year of car
  restrictions: only output an exact year if provided. If none, do not output this slot
mileage: current mileage 
 restrictions: round to the nearest 10000

Extract the slots in the following message following the rules in the schema above. Output should be formatted in YAML

----

Hello, I heard about your shop through a friend and he said you do a great job of seeing people quickly. I hit a curb in my minivan and part of the bumper detached. I don't want to replace the whole bumper, but if you can secure it in some way, that'd save my life. I would love to come in next week, Tuesday is best but I can work around your availability.

rejected:
request: repair
vehicle: minivan
preference:
    - day: Tuesday
      available: true
    
[...]
    - type: bumper
      fix: partial
-------
